Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpGoya Foods CEO Robert Unanue details the damage Kamala Harris's inflation crisis has inflicted on his company."Overall prices are up 20.5%, but let me tell you... that's fake news. For Goya, it's up more like 50%."
